  letterBodyDefault: "Whoever you are \u2014\nif you are reading this, the candle
    in the Hollow lit again.\nI did not blow it out.\nI went after the Forgotten
    Year, and I will not be back\nbefore you have settled. Polish the orbs slowly.
    Trust\nthe bread before you trust the men. And do not \u2014 do not \u2014\nopen
    the locked drawer until the cat tells you to.\n"
  letterSignatureDefault: "\u2014 Marin, Keeper of the Hollow before you"
